Complete Balance Reiki was established on the Big Island of Hawaii in 2019 where I studied Reiki and completed Reiki levels 1,2 and Master / Teacher Certification. Complete Balance Reiki is performed in the traditional teachings of Dr. Usui using the Rhyoho method. After over 25years of experience working as a Massage Therapist and Energy worker I decided to take my services to the next Level. Now offering Reiki to as many people as possible. Whether you are just looking for a healing session or aspire to use Reiki to heal yourself or assist others, Complete Balance Reiki can meet your needs. We are Now Offering Distant Reiki Healing Sessions Every Sunday. You may also contact us to schedule a One to One Distant Healing Session as well as an in-person Reiki Healing Session. As we continue to grow we will be offering Reiki Attunements both online and in-person.</w></div>

